    "Description": "I\u2019ve got people left and right askin\u2019 me if I know what happened to ~mission(TargetName). Now personally, I\u2019d be more than happy to see \u2018em gone for good, but for whatever reason they got friends in high places demanding answers.\n\nI can\u2019t spare any of my people to go on a wild goose chase, so I'm looking for the perfect candidate to go over to ~mission(Location|Address) and find out what happened to ~mission(TargetName|Last). You\u2019ll get paid if you find where they are.\n\n10 credits says they got way too high and passed out in a dark corner somewhere.\n\n-Smokey",
